Application: Cascade Double Rejected
  Description: Both cascade and restrict on the same reference must fail (TERMIN-S codes c)
Id: a1c0c1a0-cade-4a00-9000-000000000012

Identity:
  Scopes are "d.view", "d.manage"
  A "tester" has "d.view" and "d.manage"

Content called "parents":
  Each parent has a name which is text, required
  Anyone with "d.view" can view parents
  Anyone with "d.manage" can create parents

Content called "children":
  Each child has a label which is text, required
  Each child has a parent which references parents, required, cascade on delete, restrict on delete
  Anyone with "d.view" can view children
  Anyone with "d.manage" can create children
